managers.json
    route messages with manager path. Each property of the config object will be the message that will be sent
    by the client. The value will be the relative path (from app/managers) of its manager.

database.json
    configuration file for the MongoDB connection with MongoLabs:
        - port     : connection port
        - url      : url from mongolabs
        - dbName   : database name
        - user     : database user
        - password : user's password